info.name: Custom Google Logo
info.description: A simple style allowing you to define your own logo on Google websites. You can try it now with the old Google logo, or try this Lycos logo! Theme by n0x (nox). Optimal logo size: 275x95
info.additionalInfo: Customize the graphical appearance of a website you visit everyday with your own image! Make it more friendly, re-stylish it now ;) -- Get more userstyles from me! -- Firefox rules. tags: google, logo, search, ui, custom, image, stealth, edit, persona, modify, flat, design, duckduckgo, privacy, translate, dark, modern, material.
